What is TECHNOCRASHTECHNOCRASH is a single-use gadget to face and manage the interaction with technological devices in case of issues. A pocket-sized mockup of your laptop to unleash your fury, saving your money… and your liver as well! Why TECHNOCRASHEveryday life is always more characterized by frequent interactions with technological devices.What about us when technology is faulting, hampering our efforts to get the goal?TECHNOCRASH can help you saving money and avoiding stress!TECHNOCRASH - THE NEW WAY IN FRONT OF IT ISSUES SIMPLE AND EFFECTIVE, FOR IMMEDIATE RELIEF ALWAYS WITH YOU, READY FOR USE EVERYTIME & EVERYWHERE  GADGET AS WELL AS GIFT, A SMART IDEA FOR A SOURCE OF RELIEF  This campaign is focused on the creation of a pilot and 1st limited edition, hence the overall target amount is relatively small. Anyway, the % weight of the pilot mould is quite important and, given the small number of pieces, its impact over the final cost per unit is relevant.This is a first fundamental step since the success of this campaign will pave the way for the next launch of a wide-scale production of TECHNOCRASH in many thousands pieces. For this reason this first limited edition is so precious and exclusive, as a collection piece.Additional details about campaign budget allocation are reported here below.  

PRODUCTION: about 65% of campaign target is directly related to TECHNOCRASH production cost. More precisely: cost of moulds, cost of production process realization (both plants use and human job), cost of material, and finally cost of graphic printing;

MARKETING & COMMUNICATION: about 23% of the overall target is related to marketing and communication cost, needed to support the product launch phase, the promotion of TECHNOCRASH brand, the management of communication channels and tools adopted;

CROWDFUNDING: about 7% weight is related to crowdfunding campaign, in terms of platform commissions, transaction and currency exchange commissions, cost related to campaign video and pitch realization;

SHIPPING & OTHER: about 5% is related to shipping expenses and other expenses. Here included: i) packaging for delivery; ii) a partial contribute to overall shipping cost (limiting the shipping expenses charged to each single contributor when subscribing); iii) residual current expenses supporting the overall project running toward final target.
IMPORTANT NOTE: the overall target campaign DOES NOT include cost related to design phase, already funded and covered by project owners in terms both of incurred expenses and of their own time enthusiastically spent over this wonderful project. All the proposed perks consist of different mix of the following items:You can choose your preferred option among the different set of perks that have been created trying to offer a wide portfolio able to meet and fit with different needs in terms both of quantity (how many TECHNOCRASH units do I need? for me only? a gift for my friends and colleagues? a gadget for my company employees?) and mix (do I like getting the exclusive TECHNOCRASH T-shirt?).Finally, if you believe that our idea deserves a glittering future, you can also join us and supporting the campaign via a "only pledge, no reward" contribution.Anyway, please get any chance to share TECHNOCRASH campaign within your network!!! TECHNOCRASH original concept was born in 2012. From the original seed, the idea has progressively been growing up and taking shape until now, with the prototyping phase run in 2017 and the launch of this crowdfunding campaign in Spring 2018.TECHNOCRASH 1st limited edition will be delivered no later than November 2018. Afterwards, a new release will be planned with the launch of a wide-scale production of TECHNOCRASH, open to graphic customization for corporate clients as well.A new generation of products focused on human emotions and mental wellness is rising. TECHNOCRASH is the first one! This campaign is the first step along the path towards JUMPINTOP incorporation. Support this campaign and support JUMPINTOP launch as well.JUMPINTOP creates and distributes unconventional, funny and immediate solutions to overcome the setbacks and hitches often related to the chaotic rush of modern life. A series of situation-based emotional tool for mental wellness will be ready for you as easy source of relief. Everything started from a long-lasting friendship between Guido and Andrea. First many hours spent together at high school. Then the same University, getting the degree in Engineering. And in this way, between a laugh and a drink, between a successful delivery and a job lost due to a PC-crash… TECHNOCRASH starts taking shape!!!Guido and Andrea follow different career paths but they keep in contact each other and in parallel they go on working on the original idea which progressively grows up. Year after year the working group widens, getting involved friends and other cooperators, until the definition of a path for the incorporation of JUMPINTOP and the first crucial step of TECHNOCRASH launch with this crowdfunding campaign. Here you can find additional information about TECHNOCRASH technical features in terms of design, material, production process. DESIGNTECHNOCRASH design is studied in order to enable you to get the most from the interaction with this tool. It is linear and compact and it aims to provide the direct and immediate perception of a real technological device. This helps getting the quick and full identification between the mock-up and the real technological device that is not working and that is annoying you.MATERIALTECHNOCRASH material is selected aiming to get the most from the crashing act, both in terms of resistance and of sound. This is crucial to convey the right feeling to the user and to grant the best experience while crashing the tool.PRODUCTION PROCESSTECHNOCRASH is created via a specialized production process. Starting from the required parameters in terms of material (type, density, weight, color, etc.) and of shape and size, customized molds was realized to get the best result and the finest details. Moreover, a customized printing plate was created in order to reproduce even the smallest graphics. Everything to get an extraordinary result and offer you a unique experience with a TECHNOCRASH in your hands!
